com.iopipe.plugin.eventinfo

Interface EventInfoDecoder

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    APIGatewayDecoder, CloudFrontDecoder, FirehoseDecoder, KinesisDecoder, S3Decoder, ScheduledDecoder, SNSDecoder

    public interface EventInfoDecoder
    This interface represents a decoder for event types being input into the executed method and contains the information that is needed to parse fields accordingly.
